Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:01:59.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:03.72,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll take care of Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:07.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you trying to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:10.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:13.23,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You need to prepare our escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:16.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We don't have a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:19.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to get held up by Cal and waste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:21.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Therefore I'll handle this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:23.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I asked you the same question before,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:27.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but can you point your gun at her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:31.21,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:39.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:44.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Give me just a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.64,0:02:52.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:56.73,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I need your answer today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:03.24,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you can't make up your mind, I'll kill Drei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:11.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And I will also...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:14.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...save Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:31.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't let Elen point her gun at Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:33.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have to be the one to settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:36.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:38.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}Reiji...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:42.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}Reiji, I want to be with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:46.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:48.14,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:50.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Want to have lunch together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:53.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you're so occupied with Mio,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:57.24,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}it's a rare chance for you to eat lunch with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:59.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's not many we can eat with today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.82,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mio and Elen are both taking the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:04.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:07.15,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She went to school with me this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:08.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She left early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:11.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She said she wasn't feeling well this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:13.23,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey! Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:19.23,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tell us how far you've gotten with Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:32.16,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:38.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}The number you have dialed is out of range or turned off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:42.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't run, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How far have you and Mio...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:45.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hold on, this isn't the time to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you so freaked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:49.86,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you that worried about Elen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:51.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's a limit to how siscon you can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:52.96,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:55.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fifth period is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, jeez. We're going back to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:00.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:11.51,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have to turn it off during classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:13.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:18.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now, let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:25.97,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}This is a mailbox service center. You have a message.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:30.97,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You might be angry with me by the time you hear this message,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:35.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but I really think this is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:40.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You must not fight Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm the one who got Mio involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:49.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will save her even if it kills me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:50.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:53.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...you have to escape ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After I've saved her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:00.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And if...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:06.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I don't show up on time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:11.60,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}please consider me dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}That was today at 2:15 PM.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:19.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:22.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't do it, Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:29.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to lose anyone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to get anyone hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:36.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:46.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Our prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We must report to Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:58.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're putting up with this pretty well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:04.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thought you'd cry or be more upset than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:08.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm not an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:16.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You were tricked by him and dragged into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:19.35,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You should be furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you furious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.64,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}About Reiji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:29.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't talk big.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:36.17,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:40.02,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How can you hate someone so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:44.35,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're not the only one who suffered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He must have suffered too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:49.20,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:51.56,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:53.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How can I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:57.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you're truly in love with him, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:15.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're such a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:19.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Both you and Reiji are liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:27.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is everyone in this country like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:34.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Have you ever frozen out in the cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you get beaten up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:45.08,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you survive for three nights without food?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:54.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:09:01.86,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you really think nothing in this world could hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:06.60,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you think it's normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:09.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...to be the one fawned over by everybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:14.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You live in comfort and wealth in this foolish country...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:16.10,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can't possibly know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:22.24,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...about the suffering of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:25.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:30.75,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You see, I only had a single dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:34.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was burnt to ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:41.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What food were you eating to have such smooth skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:44.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tell me, little princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:47.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll teach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:50.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...the true meaning of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:57.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Helplessness engulfing your own ability to do anything at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...will be carved into your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:06.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like a wound it will stay deep in your heart for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:30.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've been waiting for you here all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:32.61,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You said you'd come home for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.85,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You promised me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.18,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:40.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.70,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:11.22,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.62,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that you, Shiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.82,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry to disturb you this late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:38.61,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm guessing you have bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:41.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This matter pertains to Fujieda Mio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:46.64,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As I arrived late, she has been subjected to her current hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:52.14,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We've reached the height of the conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:56.90,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm fully aware of my responsibility in this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:12:01.92,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, before anything else, saving Mio-san is my primary objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:07.35,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For that I ask your permission to mobilize the Godou family's retainers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:11.66,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are the ringleaders those Americans?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:15.67,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is Mio still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:17.92,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, it was confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:21.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then it's not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.77,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't mobilize the Godou family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:28.34,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Leave the matter to the foreigners.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.80,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:34.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If the clan moves out, we might as well announce it to all of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:41.28,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why would the Goudo clan be in frantic disarray for the sake of a single girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:44.15,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}People would want to know the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:49.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You couldn't do anything about it. Taking responsibility isn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:50.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.88,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I said no, Shiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:58.25,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There is no relation between the Fujieda household and ourselves and it must stay that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.57,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Neither now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:02.71,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...nor in days past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:08.58,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Listen now, don't take any action until Mio is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:14.23,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As long as we aren't told a ransom or threatened as a clan, there's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:18.52,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thank you for your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:25.55,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shiga, being part of the mafia is nothing but a heavy burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:29.24,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Especially when you try to protect something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:34.68,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Guns and blades can only slay and smash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:37.29,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They can't protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.25,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:42.37,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll keep it in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:48.23,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When I appear in a play I've written,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:51.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I always act my own part.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:59.51,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Play and stage have passed the climax and are about to reach the denouement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:03.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The creation of the perfect soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:06.75,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein was my first piece of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:09.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The experimental ones were Zwei and Drei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:15.75,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Brought forth by them is the final product, the actors presenting the epilogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:24.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Zahlenschwestern, devoid of fear or mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:29.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They are machines carrying death like faithful hounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:36.60,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Both the Godou clan and Inferno are nothing but my tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:44.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will dispatch them once Drei is cornered by Ein and Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:48.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The chapter where they all appear will come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:54.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You, the Zahlenschwestern, are included in the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:58.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I await the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:04.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...when the bell announces the curtain call.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:50.07,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Drei, I assume.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.31,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:56.64,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's meet where nobody can disrupt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:16:00.32,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll put an end to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:04.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:08.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Leave him behind, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:11.60,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.66,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is she talking to Reiji-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:20.66,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay, that place is fine. 3 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:26.07,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you know those rundown buildings opposite Shinokura High School?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:27.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The old girl's dormitory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:29.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, that's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:32.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can find Mio there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:35.17,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bring some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:41.31,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you've woken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:58.74,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Forget everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:06.35,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm not a woman you should have a grudge against.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:12.89,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even without you there are already plenty of others who hold a grudge against me and can't forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:16.71,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I probably won't live long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:20.76,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When my time comes, I will go straight to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:23.98,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:47.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where were you? I was worr-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Mio-san's classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:18:00.51,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She took the day off, so I came over to bring the printout.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mio took the day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:04.83,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:05.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:08.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well then, I'm leaving again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:09.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:11.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Umm, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:24.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, it's nothing. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:26.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:33.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.21,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:44.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:47.46,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There is no longer a reason to keep it a secret from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:51.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So please call me "Ein".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:54.44,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Keep it a secret"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:56.67,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:18:59.22,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I brought you a change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:00.81,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:02.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who did...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Drei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:04.87,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Drei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:08.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you referring to Cal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:10.71,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}People have called her that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.64,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You heard the story from Drei, I assume.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:22.55,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is it really true... that you and Reiji-san... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:26.47,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes. We are assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:30.61,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No way... it can't be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:33.73,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, but can you go home by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:36.23,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can call the cops with this if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:38.74,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:42.18,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal left before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:47.15,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She said something about putting an end to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:50.19,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's probably trying to kill Reiji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:52.51,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:54.17,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:57.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then, she was calling...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:00.41,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you going to fight her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:06.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is there nothing I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:08.72,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I love Reiji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:13.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd do anything for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:16.54,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that still not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:18.32,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can't I be together with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:22.83,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your emotions might be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:26.76,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But you cannot defeat Drei with your feelings alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:32.64,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I don't kill Drei, she will kill Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:38.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Preventing that is my responsibility, not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:44.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you want to be useful for him, stay here for a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:48.46,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you do that, his chances of survival will increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:51.85,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:54.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did he lie to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:55.84,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, he did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:01.10,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The one who dragged you into this is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:05.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji isn't someone who can fake crying or laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:11.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you have ever seen him laugh or cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:14.19,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}they must have been his true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:31.21,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ever since you called me Elen,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:35.92,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}my life has been devoted only to protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.07,0:21:40.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want you to live, I want you to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.36,0:21:55.47,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you survive, that would be proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:21:58.37,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...that I ever lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:36.67,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:42.95,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At least it would be if I could find the unlikely salvation I dream of.
